        "Use an energy flow diagram showing energy input (heating, magnets, cooling) versus energy output (fusion power) to visualize the Q factor challenge",
        "Sentence frames: 'The biggest bottleneck is __ because the model shows that when __ increases, __ also increases, which limits __'"
