        ("ELA", "Write a policy brief for Congress arguing either for increased federal fusion funding or for redirecting that funding to proven renewable energy technologies, using evidence from your model to support your position"),
        ("History", "Research the history of fusion energy predictions from 1950 to today — why did each generation predict commercial fusion within 30 years, and what did they underestimate?")
